{"code":0,"msg":"ok","data":{"article":{"authorCode":"admin","authorName":"孙天骁","classify":"观点类","content":"<p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">我敬佩这个世界，神秘的宇宙中存在我们千千万万形态各异的生物和人。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">我对一切感到不解，因为我还不懂我的存在是为了什么，大家的存在都是为了什么。为什么会有这个地球，为什么会有我的学校、我的班级，为什么会有百度。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">我在寻找快乐，但是我还很弱小，我并不满足我现在的状况。甚至我可以说，一切都糟透了......</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">我在追求满足，但周围的一切还不能让我满足。甚至，我遭遇的不幸会比我取得的成就更加刻骨铭心。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">曾几何时，我追求一种统一与没有缺憾的原则。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><a href=\"http://tieba.baidu.com/f?kw=%CB%EF%CC%EC%E6%E7&amp;tp=0\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">孙天骁吧</span></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">的另外两位吧主不是我最熟悉的网友。他们甚至几乎不来我的贴吧，几乎已不在我的贴吧世界里活跃。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">面对形形色色的网友，我有迷惑。面对形形色色的同学，我有迷惑。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">为什么lipeiyi2006 百百MP3会有那样的思想呢？我不懂。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">为什么李雷、王芳会有那样的思想呢？我也不懂。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">我所努力的都是为了什么？我真不想和你们闹矛盾，可你们都在抛弃我。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">为什么...你们不能理解我，我也无法彻底理解你们&hellip;&hellip;</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">幻想有一天，能实现交往融洽、学习进步、编程技术上升一个新的台阶。但一切似乎还很远&hellip;&hellip;</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">机器猫吧在宇宙、红龙、镇魂当吧主时，他们很像兄弟。</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">而我的则不&hellip;&hellip;</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">唉...一切什么时候能好起来呢？</span></span></span></p><p><span style=\"font-family: '微软雅黑'; \"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 51, 0); \"><span style=\"font-size: smaller; \">哆啦A梦保佑我。。。。。</span></span></span></p>","createTime":"2013-01-30 20:31:28","customCoverKey":"","id":5,"isGood":false,"isTop":false,"publicState":0,"replyCount":0,"state":0,"tags":["感想与感悟"],"title":"追求统一与没有缺憾的生活","urlCode":"26B8Q1CU8P","viewCount":751,"viewGroup":-1,"authPassed":true},"author":{"exists":true,"name":"孙天骁","code":"admin","alias":"stx","description":"一个内心丰富的人","homepageUrl":"/u/stx","group":5,"groupName":"站长","isLocked":false,"gender":1,"avatarUrl":"/s/user/FufL-vSFO5eM1we1mxdfYHKH9tfK.jpg","realName":"孙天骁","refBaike":"","isManager":true,"isMe":true,"isLover":false,"introduction":"","joinTime":"2015-02-11 21:45:00"}}}